headline: Why Ulta (ULTA) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of beauty, cosmetics, and personal care retailer Ulta Beauty (NASDAQ:ULTA) jumped 3.1% in the afternoon session after JP Morgan analyst Christopher Horvers maintained an "Overweight" rating on the company while raising the price target. The financial firm increased its price target on Ulta Beauty's stock to $606 from $600.
